{"tid":376792,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想搞個party俾各位巴絲玩","createTime":"2017-08-27T08:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T10:18:27.000Z","uid":56763,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2519a08651d0862682fd24cf41a458ab678b6395","tid":376792,"uid":56763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac開post <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小妹今年讀緊大學，之前係到都試過搞一次party，因為想再練習下自己搞event同做Mc嘅技巧，依家得到幾位朋友既幫忙，肯幫手做搞手，但唯一係差左出席活動既巴絲打 <br />\n<br />\n所以上黎問問，有冇巴絲打願意出席今次活動 <br />\n<br />\n我會book場，已經揀定咗幾間， <br />\n可能會係book party room之後叫到會， <br />\n又或者BBQ <br />\n<br />\n會有啲小遊戲同大家玩吓咁 <br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇巴絲打有興趣 <br />\n<br />\n時間：暫定9月24日（星期日）夜晚 <br />\n名額：巴打8位，絲打8位 <br />\n地點：TBC (多數九龍旺區） <br />\n費用： <br />\n巴打250 <br />\n絲打100 <br />\n（包場同包食，巴打貴啲因為用黎補貼絲打，希望多啲絲打參加） <br />\n<br />\n利申: 冇賺任何錢，只求唔蝕同唔好嫌棄我冇咩經驗 <br />\n同希望巴絲打玩完後可以比返feedback <br />\n<br />\n有意就填下面張google form啦 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScgWBdH7DJuf28FLIhWImS3aW9ss0HrYHjByN8Nr1ggaDrk5g/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScgWBdH7DJuf28FLIhWImS3aW9ss0HrYHjByN8Nr1ggaDrk5g%2Fviewform&d=ABAp%2BiCMwl6VFSawRmSdZdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=171a4a8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScgWBdH7DJuf28FLIhWImS3aW9ss0HrYHjByN8Nr1ggaDrk5g/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"3994183fb49331d83b8bdb92280c79331881fe60","tid":376792,"uid":20942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"以為係有錢人船p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80ce7cab6fb9dd43b7562881fc5b4de2fee9f1f","tid":376792,"uid":134723,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5jtk3z2u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5jtk3z2u&h=ffe27505&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8f9ea228c54b3396188709ce788a61fda0e